Name: This is the EVA TTS, Speech Synthesis product
Text: This is the EVA TTS, Speech Synthesis product

Name: You can use this product to set the animation timings of existing sound files.
Text: You can use this product to set the animation timings of existing sound files.

Name: Or you can use the Text-toSpeech functionality to create new sound files.
Text: Or you can use the Text-toSpeech functionality to create new sound files.

Name: Use the controls on your right to fine tune the timings.
Text: Use the controls on your right to fine tune the timings.

Name: You can also use time dilation controls on your left to slow down the animation.
Text: You can also use time dilation controls on your left to slow down the animation.

Name: you can use any Microsoft voice that is installed on your computer.
Text: you can use any Microsoft voice that is installed on your computer.

Name: For special effects, you can change the avatar skin or accompanying particle by using the controls on your top right.
Text: For special effects, you can change the avatar skin or accompanying particle by using the controls on your top right.

Name: You can even change the light color or intensity for additional effect.
Text: You can even change the light color or intensity for additional effect.

Name: When you select the save option, the wave file as well as the phoneme timings are stored in files for future use.
Text: When you select the save option, the wave file as well as the phoneme timings are stored in files for future use.
